latestIgtvVideos.title: looking back at a video from 24th Jan 2020
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hey,
if you are another person as clueless as me, (extra brownie points if you have anxiety), who questions your existence and undermines your ability on a daily basis. this video is from 24th Jan 2020, when I was clueless about the tasks I was taking up.
Update:
the design collection mentioned in the video turned out to be my best work in college. I graduated with a score of 8.88, which is my topmost (never been too bright in college and it's totally fine). 
also the same design collection got me an opportunity to work with a firm,  that they mentioned and appreciated my passion and new ideas (which were considered weird by many). 
I also happen to bag the job and get placed, which makes me the first person from my department to officially get placed. Touch wood!
(This video was meant to go as a compilation of my design collection works on my YouTube channel).
.
thankyou @chinkalpareek for tagging along and making things possible for me and making me see my worth.
(pardon all the grammatical errors. Those were out of sheer excitement and stress)

latestIgtvVideos.title: 2 WAYS TO STYLE A SAREE
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Quarantined awaybfrom my wardrobe, this one's all about the series of experimentation I do with my mom's Sarees. If you are another person looking forward to experiment for a quarantine shoot, this one is for you.
These styles aren't inspired from anyone, and are completely my original experiments. Thus if anyone's trying out the same,
You can tag me, send it to me or use the hashtag #stylingnormally so that I can find your video/post and give a repost or a shout out
take care y'all! 💕
